===Etymology===
From {{m|en|Mag}}, a nickname for {{m|en|Margaret}} that was used to denote a [[chatterer]], + archaic {{m|en|pie|id=magpie|t=magpie}}, from {{der|en|fro|pie}}, from {{der|en|la|pīca}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*(s)peyk-||woodpecker, magpie}}.

